# SociallyFounded - GitHub Repository Structure

This document outlines the recommended structure for the SociallyFounded GitHub repository, aligning with our component-based architecture and development approach.

## Repository Setup

### Main Branches

- `main` - Production-ready code
- `develop` - Development branch for integration
- `feature/[name]` - Feature branches

